610
00:41:36,790 --> 00:41:38,920
Kau sedang tidak main-main di tempat lain, 'kan?

611
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:40,580
Tidak!

612
00:41:41,220 --> 00:41:44,920
Aku... pindah ke asrama rumah sakit...

613
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:47,140
